scenes.description: Elizabeth and her team prepare for the Speed Block challenge.
The team must perform poses to disarm the bomb.
Elizabeth tackles another complex block puzzle.
Elizabeth disarms the bomb with a tongue twister.
Elizabeth celebrates her success with a freestyle rap.
The bomb explodes, leaving Elizabeth charred, but she earns 10 points.
The team discusses the challenge, and Elizabeth heads for a shower.
Elizabeth returns refreshed and calls for her team.
